These are Puzzles for 3x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-1::.
Nationality: colombian, mexican
Pet: cat, hamster
City: berlin, miami
1. Pet:cat is on the right of City:berlin##1
2. Nationality:mexican is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| Nationality   | mexican    | colombian |
| Pet         | hamster | cat    |
| City     | berlin     | miami      |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-2::.
Beverage: mirinda, sprite
Food: pumpkin, strawberry
Color: blood-red, coral
1. Color:coral is on the left of Beverage:mirinda##1
2. Food:pumpkin is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |
| Beverage      | sprite  | mirinda   |
| Food   | strawberry | pumpkin  |
| Color     | coral   | blood-red |

 #################################
 
