2. Music-Genre:punk is on the left or right of Music-Genre:soul##3
3. Food:pepper is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Food    | radish | pepper     |
| City     | marseilles | liverpool |
| Music-Genre   | soul | punk    |

